casebody.data:
In re Harry JACOBS, Debtor. No. 5334. Circuit Court of Appeals, Seventh Circuit. Oct. 31, 1934.

Before EVANS, SPARKS, and FITZHENRY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On motion of counsel for appellant, it is now here ordered, adjudged, and decreed by this court that this appeal (7 F. Supp. 749) be, and the same is hereby, dismissed, with costs.
